      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RADIANT ETHICS (3) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at Bulli behind Desi's Dream (19.50) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Leading chance again. LAKOTA COURTNEY (2) had been in super honest form hitting the frame two times on end before finishing fifth (22.86) at this track last time. Worth another chance. REAL EXPRESS (1) finds it hard to break through. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing second (22.34) at this track. Has a good record here including two wins. Can feature again. SAVVY LAD (7) racing over this course and distance brings the best out in him.",
